{"id":3639,"date":"2012-07-12T21:31:14","date_gmt":"2012-07-13T01:31:14","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=3639"},"modified":"2019-05-19T13:11:41","modified_gmt":"2019-05-19T09:11:41","slug":"trimming-moustache-let-beard-grow","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/12\/trimming-moustache-let-beard-grow\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Sunnah: Trimming moustache, letting beard grow"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Be different from the idolaters. Let the beard grow and trim the moustache<\/strong>.\u201d Whenever Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, performed the Hajj or Umrah pilgrimage, he would grab hold of his beard and cut what was beyond his grasp.<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5553, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 259<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun\u00a0<\/strong><\/em><em><strong>Alayhi<\/strong><\/em> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p>Al-Qadi &#8216;Iyad said, \u201cIt is discouraged\u00a0to cut, shave, or trim the beard.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Fath\u0323 al-Ba\u0304ri\u0304 5553<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e <strong>\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0641\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0634\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0643\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0648\u064e\u0641\u0650\u0651\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0650\u0651\u062d\u064e\u0649 \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0641\u064f\